channel.title: 614 Sources
channel.description:
Whenever I use a 614 source it's always edited and barely anything works, so the one I just got you can't even walk up stairs.
Is there anyway that I can get an Unedited 614 source that I can just start playing on? And everything work on, like shops, stairs and all that.?
PS: Any idea on how to decrypt and edit a .SER file would be helpful too.
